3.37.91 - Sep 10, 2020
======================

Changes since 3.37.90

  - Connections got enrolled in the GNOME translation infrastructure
  - Moved to the GNOME/ Gitlab namespace
  - Added/updated/fixed translations:
    - Greek
    - Portuguese
    - French
    - Persian
    - Turkish
    - Hungarian
    - Slovenian
    - Spanish
    - Korean
    - Galician
    - Chinese (China)
    - Slovak
    - Danish
    - Czech
    - Serbian
    - Indonesian
    - Croatian
    - Catalan
    - Lithuanian
    - German
    - Ukrainian
    - Polish
    - Swedish
    - Brazilian Portuguese
    - Finnish
    - Basque
    - Japanese
    - British English
    - Friulian

